msgid "Blocking Time Upload Purpose"
msgstr ""

#: admin/sip-options.php:316
msgid ""
"Specifies which upload purposes allow a blocking time to be selected or applied.\n"
"Only the upload purposes defined here will enable users to set a blocking time during upload. Make sure to use a comma separated list of one or more defined upload purposes from the previous selection."
msgstr ""

#: admin/sip-options.php:318
msgid "Blocking Time Calculate"
msgstr ""

#: admin/sip-options.php:319
msgid ""
"Defines how the blocking time is calculated by default.\n"
"This setting allows you to specify a rule used to automatically determine the end of the blocking period, e.g. year of birth + 100 years."
msgstr ""

#: admin/sip-options.php:321
msgid "Right Transfer Text"
msgstr ""

#: admin/sip-options.php:322
msgid ""
"Defines the text displayed to users regarding the transfer of rights.\n"
"The content should provide information about the donation agreement between the users and the website and clearly explain the legal terms of the transfer."
msgstr ""

